info.author: The NDEx Project
info.description: # ndex-python-utilities In addition to python, these utilities require some additional modules. To install these modules, type the following commands: ```shell pip install requests pip install requests-toolbelt pip install ndex ``` Utility Scripts: In all scripts that have arguments username and password, these will be the username and password for the NDEx account that you are using. upload-to-ndex.py ```shell python upload-to-ndex.py ``` Where directory contains all of the network files you want to upload. create_network_from_tsv.py ```shell python create_network_from_tsv.py ``` change_network_descriptions.py change_network_versions.py make_networks_public.py make_networks_private.py delete_all_networks.py get_user_account_statistics.py download_pc_pathways.py ```shell download_pc_pathways.py ```
info.name: ndex-utils
info.summary: NDEx Python utilities.  Includes file conversion and importing functions
